# Cursor Rules — The Golden Forest (lorien.cloud)

## Source of Truth
AGENTS.md — read it before making any code changes.

## Project Stack
- Docusaurus 3.x, React 19, MDX, CSS Modules (no TypeScript)
- No test framework — verify with `yarn start` + manual check
- `make check` validates MDX syntax

## Key Conventions
- Function components only (React 19 hooks)
- CSS Modules with camelCase classes; use `clsx()` for conditionals
- Imports order: React → external → @docusaurus/@theme → local → CSS module
- Components: PascalCase directories, registered in src/theme/MDXComponents/index.js
- Wrap browser-dependent logic in `<BrowserOnly>`
- Conventional Commits: feat(scope): desc

## Critical Rules
- onBrokenLinks: 'throw' — always verify internal links
- MDX: escape < > as &lt; &gt; outside code blocks
- Card hrefs resolve from page URL (trailingSlash: true), not file system
- clientModules run at page load — guard with `typeof document !== 'undefined'`
